content.html: Prince Harry reveals Daenerys Targaryen as his comfort character during his lowest moments in new memoir ‘Spare’ “Her story resembles mine in many ways. She is so inspiring to me. Just like Daenerys I will take back what was stolen from me. I will take it.”

Prince Harry reveals Daenerys Targaryen as his comfort character during his lowest moments in new memoir ‘Spare’

“Her story resembles mine in many ways. She is so inspiring to me. Just like Daenerys I will take back what was stolen from me. I will take it.”
